aims-os-desktop-dev (2.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Carved out of aims-os-desktop. Holds the Java /
    Android / Web / Rust / Containers stack (default-jdk, Gradle, Kotlin,
    PHP, Composer, adb/fastboot, Docker, Podman, kubectl, Ansible,
    rustup) — about 2 GB on disk. Kept out of the live ISO; available
    on demand via the first-boot wizard or apt.

